SQL_STMT_U.val: select ACCT_ADMNO, ACCT_CLNTNO, COUNT(ACCT_DATE) from :1/acct where ACCT_ADMNO=:2 and ACCT_CLNTNO=:3 and ACCT_DATE = ':4' group by ACCT_ADMNO, ACCT_CLNTNO
select ACCT_ADMNO, ACCT_CLNTNO, MAX(ACCT_DATE) from :1/acct where ACCT_ADMNO=:2 and ACCT_CLNTNO=:3 and ACCT_DATE < ':4' group by ACCT_ADMNO, ACCT_CLNTNO
select ACCT_ADMNO, ACCT_CLNTNO, MIN(ACCT_DATE) from :1/acct where ACCT_ADMNO=:2 and ACCT_CLNTNO=:3 and ACCT_DATE > ':4' group by ACCT_ADMNO, ACCT_CLNTNO
